      • createMap

        <K,V> ConcurrentMap<K,V> createMap(String name)
        Retrieve a map identified by a name. Each time createMap is invoked with a name, the associated map is returned. If there is no map for the name, a new one is created.
        Type Parameters:
        K - key type.
        V - value type.
        Parameters:
        name - name that identifies the map
        Returns:
        concurrent map.
